  "tosSection1Para1": "By creating an account, accessing, or using the {appName} mobile application (\"the Service\"), you agree to be bound by these Termos of Service (\"TerTermos If you do not agree to these TTermos you must not access or use the Service.",
  "tosSection1Para2": "The Service is provided by {producer} (\"we\", \"us\", or \"our\"). These Termos form a legally binding agreement between you and us.",
